OL,3,CEast Londoners Kane and Beckham tie on
OL,4,Cfootball appearances for their country
OL,6,FEngland captain Harry Kane will move
OL,7,Flevel with David Beckham in third on
OL,8,Fthe list of all-time appearances for
OL,9,Fhis country when he leads England out
OL,10,Fagainst Croatia in the World Cup
OL,11,Fopener in Dallas on Wednesday.
OL,13,FThe two east Londoners will be tied on
OL,14,F115 caps.
OL,16,FHarry Kane was just 10 years old when
OL,17,Fhe met the former Manchester United
OL,18,Fmidfielder during a visit to his
OL,19,Fschool in 2005.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
