OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781874674
OL,3,CEast Londoners Kane and Beckham tie on
OL,4,Cfootball appearances for their country
OL,6,FThe England captain says being from
OL,7,Fthe same area as Beckham meant he was
OL,8,Fa huge inspiration.
OL,10,F"He was a hero of mine growing up.
OL,12,F"I was a massive England fan and him
OL,13,Fbeing England captain, he was a big
OL,14,Finspiration to me, just the way he
OL,15,Fworked on the pitch, but also how he
OL,16,Fwas off the pitch as well.
OL,18,F"We were from the same area, we went
OL,19,Fto the same school, so he was a hero
OL,20,Fof mine.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781874674
OL,3,CEast Londoners Kane and Beckham tie on
OL,4,Cfootball appearances for their country
OL,6,F"We've had contact, not recently, but
OL,7,Fobviously over the previous
OL,8,Ftournaments. We exchange messages
OL,9,Fevery now and then and after winning
OL,10,Ftrophies or whatever it might be, we
OL,11,Fkeep in contact."
OL,13,FThe Bayern Munich striker continued:
OL,15,F"For me personally to be where I am
OL,16,Fnow, it's always hard to really take
OL,17,Fit all in.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
