PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781874674
OL,3,CEast Londoners Kane and Beckham tie on
OL,4,Cfootball appearances for their country
OL,6,F"When you're young, especially at that
OL,7,Fage, I think I was 10-11 years old,
OL,8,Fyou just have dreams and aspirations
OL,9,Fof trying to become a footballer.
OL,11,F"Now to be hopefully making 115 caps
OL,12,Fand going to my sixth tournament,
OL,13,Fbeing captain for as long as I have,
OL,14,Fthe goalscoring record, all these
OL,15,Fthings that I've managed to achieve
OL,16,Falong the way are extremely proud
OL,17,Fthings, but things I won't truly be
OL,18,Fable to appreciate until whenever I
OL,19,Fstop because as you guys know it's
OL,20,Fjust about the next thing, the next
OL,21,Fmoment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781874674
OL,3,CEast Londoners Kane and Beckham tie on
OL,4,Cfootball appearances for their country
OL,6,F"Being better, improving, and that
OL,7,Fwill be my mindset until the day that
OL,8,FI stop playing."
OL,10,FEngland never made it past the semi-
OL,11,Ffinal when Beckham was in the team,
OL,12,Fbut this crop's chances are enhanced
OL,13,Fby having Kane in their team, fresh
OL,14,Ffrom scoring a mountain of goals for
OL,15,FBayern Munich last term as he
OL,16,Fplundered 61 in 51 games.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
