OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781874674
OL,3,CEast Londoners Kane and Beckham tie on
OL,4,Cfootball appearances for their country
OL,6,FThe 32-year-old helped Munich to a
OL,7,Fsecond successive Bundesliga title and
OL,8,Fadded the German Cup as well, and he
OL,9,Fbelieves his form in Germany has led
OL,10,Fto people taking him more seriously.
OL,12,FHarry Kane spoke of winning his first
OL,13,Ftrophies as a player:
OL,15,F"For me personally, to have that
OL,16,Fweight off my shoulders is important.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1781874674
OL,3,CEast Londoners Kane and Beckham tie on
OL,4,Cfootball appearances for their country
OL,6,F"Especially this year having the
OL,7,Ftrophies and having the cup final
OL,8,Fwhere I scored a hat-trick, my first
OL,9,Fbig moment in a final ` I think that
OL,10,Fis only going to help me as a player.
OL,12,F"Also, I think the perception around
OL,13,Fme has probably changed in the last
OL,14,Ffew years.
OL,16,F"The fact that I've won those trophies
OL,17,Fmeans I'm seen a bit differently from
OL,18,Fthe outside or by people around, and
OL,19,Fmaybe even team-mates, I'm not quite
OL,20,Fsure."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/7
